						<p class="faq"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>How the $%&amp;(# do I plan an event with no money?!</p>
						<p>You could ask each member that joins to pay dues ($5-$15) to cover basic costs like flyers and other promotional materials. Sometimes people have to put up a few dollars to plan the event, but make sure you charge an entrance fee so you’re guaranteed to make that money back. See our guide to planning an event on the cheap <a href="http://secretsauce.spoonuniversity.com/plan-an-event">here</a>.<p class="faq">If we’re not planning an event, what do we do each week?</p>
						<p>Come up with smaller biweekly campaigns, centered around flyering, tabling, charity work, fundraisers, etc. See our list of free or low cost marketing ideas <a href="marketing/business-director/free_ideas">here</a>.</p>
